text.section:
An individual is eligible to participate in the program if the individual is eligible for membership in a retirement system or a pension system and is:
a member of the faculty of an employing institution;
a professional employee at a community college or regional community college established under Title 16 of the Education Article;
an employee of the University System of Maryland who is in a position designated as exempt under a policy adopted by the University System of Maryland Board of Regents;
an employee of Morgan State University who is in a position designated as professional or administrative by the Board of Regents of Morgan State University;
an employee of St. Mary's College of Maryland who is in a position determined by the Board of Trustees of the College to be a professional or faculty position; or
an employee of the Maryland Higher Education Commission who is in a position determined by the Secretary of Higher Education to be a professional position.
